channel.title: Need help putting my RSPS 317 SERVER ONLINE!
channel.description:
Hello everyone, I need help putting my RSPS 317 server online.
The only problem is that whenever someone tries to log onto my RSPS, they get an error message stating "Sorry, loading char profile please try again." NOTE: I PORT FORWARDED AND GOT A NO-IP. (AND I TRIPLE CHECKED THEM)
Can someone SKYPE or TEAMVIEW me?
Thanks a lot.
Skype: Pedobearsson (Max Bulgatz) (PREFERRED) TeamViewer: 356 120 580 PASS : 7308

item.title: Need help putting my RSPS 317 SERVER ONLINE!

item.description:
@heatrn11 wrote:

[quote=“mattyboi1234, post:6, topic:431043”]i made my first rsps ever 2 days ago
i already have 150 pounds in donations and 100+ players i’ve put 50 pounds into the server so
its not that hard figure it out.[/quote]
You don’t have 100+ active players, you might have 100+ created characters, but I’m pretty sure a Low beginner isn’t able to 100+ players within 2 days, I’ve been trying to get 50 players on my friends server for a month, which only has 30 active players.
